"Number 2208 is a combination of the vibrations of number 2 appearing twice, amplifying its influences, the attributes of number 0, and the energies of number 8.\tNumber 2\tbrings balance and harmony, partnerships and relationships, adaptability, diplomacy and co-operation, encouragement, duality, faith and trust and serving your\tsoul mission\t. Number 2 appears twice, relating it to the\tMaster Number 22\t(Master Builder); the number of philanthropy and service to humanity. Number 22 is the number of\tArchangel Raphael\tand resonates with vision, practicality and common sense.\tNumber 0\tmagnifies and amplifies the energies of the numbers it appears with, and resonates with the Universal Energies, and stands for potential and/or choice,\tdeveloping your spiritual aspects\tand listening to your intuition and higher-self.\tNumber 8\tpromotes personal power and self-confidence, discernment and good judgement, giving and receiving,\tinner-wisdom\t, truth and integrity, decisiveness and efficiency. Number 8 is also the number of\tkarma\t(the\tUniversal Spiritual Law of Karma\t).\tAngel Number 2208 is a powerful message of self-belief, faith and trust. You have worked steadily towards achieving long-term goals and aspirations and have used your personal integrity and wisdom to their utmost. Stay focused, balanced and at peace and know that all is going to Divine right order and in Divine right time. Trust that your desired results will manifest in your life.\tAngel Number 2208 relates to your personal spirituality, inner-strength and tenacity and pursuing your\tlife purpose\t. Stay focused upon achieving both your long and short term goals and have faith and trust in your skills, talents and abilities and you will find success in all that you put your mind and efforts towards. Your\tpositive affirmations\tand optimistic outlook will manifest wonderful blessings into your life and the\tangels\tare helping you to recognize and acknowledge the Divine light within yourself and others.\tAngel Number 2208 suggests that you have been working from your heart and soul to help, assist and serve others, and you have been serving your\tlife mission\tand\tsoul purpose\twith passion and commitment. You have found balance and harmony within yourself and this is being reflected outwards to others. The\tangels\tapplaud you in your efforts and fully support and encourage you to continue on your current path. \tAngel Number 2208 may also be an indication that it is time for you to consider beginning a\tspiritually-based profession\t, practice and/or career or heart-based service.  Use your strengths and talents to uplift and enlighten others through serving humanity in compassionate and loving ways.\tNumber 2208 relates to\tnumber 3\t(2+2+0+8=12, 1+2=3) and\tAngel Number 3\t.\t*\tJoanne Walmsley\tSacred Scribes\tNUMEROLOGY\t- The Vibration and Energy of Numbers"
